<template>

  <el-table :data="tableData">
    <el-table-column prop="date" label="Date" width="140">
    </el-table-column>
    <el-table-column prop="name" label="Name" width="120">

    <el-table-column prop="address" label="Address">
    </el-table-column>
  </el-table>

</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "MainContent",
  data() {
    const item = {
      date: '2016-05-02',
      name: 'Tom',
      address: 'No. 189, Grove St, Los Angeles'
    };
    return {
      tableData: Array(10).fill(item)
    }
  },
  methods: {
    loadGet() {
      this.$axios.get(this.$httpUrl+'/user/list').then(res => {
        console.log(res)
      })
    },
    loadPost() {
      this.$axios.post('http://localhost:8090/user/list').then(res => {
        console.log(res)
      })
    },
  },

  beforeMount() {
    this.loadGet()
  }

}
</script>
